import React from 'react'; import { PERFORMANCE_METRICS } from '../data/mockData'; const PerformanceDashboard = ({ metrics = PERFORMANCE_METRICS }) => (
Total Inspections
{metrics.total_inspections}

{metrics.pending_calls}
